    <title>Stay protected, by getting the correct life and sickness insurance for your needs</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://www.strongmortgagesolutions.co.uk/stay-protected" />
    <link rel="enclosure" type="image/jpeg" href="https://cdn.website-editor.net/8bcbeef3af594fa88fa17bd170046772/dms3rep/multi/mortgage-broker-in-bristol-life-insurance-protect-yourself.jpg" length="204437" />
    <author>
      <name />
